name: Feed The Cat (AlexSowT)
description:
Hi all, thanks for playing my first Game Jam submission!

This is a game about feeding a cat and building up score. You must go out into the middle to catch fish, and then back to the edges to deposit the bones. The more you catch, the more score you'll get!

Be careful however, the more you eat, the slower you'll go, and maybe another surprise is in store.

Controls - A and D to move, SPACE to deposit what you've eaten into the boxes.

All credits can be found in game in the About Me page, please give it a read.
